      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i'm just spinning my wheels. every time i think i finally got things together—like i found a decent job or started feeling okay again—it just falls apart. it's always the same pattern. i'm so tired of fighting the same battles over and over and getting nowhere. it feels like there's no way out of this cycle.",
