    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "small changes dont even matter though. a tiny change doesnt break the loop, it just delays the next time it all breaks down. it's like being stuck in a room where the walls just keep closing in every time i take a step forward. there isn't a \"manageable action\" for this. it's just... it's constant.",
