      "role": "user",
      "content": "letting go of the fight feels like the only thing left. but every time i try to just \"let go,\" i just end up back where i started a week later. the loop is too strong. the only way to actually stop the pressure and make it stop for good is to break the cycle permanently. it's the only way out.",
